{{version031}}
{{flavour|Harms an undead creature greatly by interfering with the forces binding it together.}}

'''Dispel Undead Range''' is a monster-only spell that functions similarly to [[Dispel Undead]], but has a range of 4. Monsters with this spell are exceptionally dangerous to characters that are [[undead]] (either naturally or through use of a [[talisman of death]]) because there is no way to avoid or resist the spell's damage. Kill them quickly and try to keep other creatures between you.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*The ranged version of Dispel Undead was introduced in [[0.25]]. Prior to this version, the player and monsters could cast regular Dispel Undead from range 5.

[[Category:Monster spells]]
